docs.mods_abstract_s: Looking north from south of West Pender. Left are the Fairfield Building and Wilson Building. New post office is under construction and at the end of the street is the CPR depot. Wagons, streetcars, a car, and pedestrians, including two Sikh men. Also exists as a lantern slide (66979). Vancouver Public Library. Accession number 6781
